## ⚠️ Common Issues

* Missing `requirements.txt`
* Wrong file name (must be `application.py`)
* Dependency errors
* Port mismatch

---

## 💸 Cost Management

To avoid AWS charges, terminate the environment after testing:

```bash
eb terminate
```

